00:28:11.935 --> 00:28:13.175
- What?
- A bug.

341
00:28:13.736 --> 00:28:15.416
- A bug?
- A flying bug.

342
00:28:15.496 --> 00:28:16.414
Can I see it?

343
00:28:16.534 --> 00:28:18.574
I think it came
in the ventilation shaft.

344
00:28:18.654 --> 00:28:21.255
