French Special Forces.

576
00:50:45.122 --> 00:50:47.282
I understand you had a corporate theft.

577
00:50:47.362 --> 00:50:49.682
Yes, that's what I told
the Defense Department.

578
00:50:49.761 --> 00:50:53.560
