580
00:50:56.681 --> 00:51:00.240
You have the Defense Department
at your disposal. Why call me?

581
00:51:00.319 --> 00:51:02.799
Because their
investment here is sizeable.

582
00:51:02.879 --> 00:51:06.038
One hundred and twenty
billion dollars, to be exact.

583
00:51:06.118 --> 00:51:08.919
And I can't afford
for them to reconsider.

584
00:51:08.999 --> 00:51:11.158
What you tell them
is your business, doctor.

585
00:51:11.238 --> 00:51:14.038
I am in the business
of keeping my clients' confidence.

586
00:51:14.118 --> 00:51:15.558
Good.

587
00:51:19.837 --> 00:51:22.078
Two of our products have escaped.

588
00:51:22.118 --> 00:51:24.996
Impressive,
considering they're vegetative.

589
00:51:25.076 --> 00:51:27.836
Well, after several years
of trial and error,

590
00:51:27.876 --> 00:51:30.154
we discovered that
without consciousness,

591
00:51:30.234 --> 00:51:35.434
without human experience,
emotion, without life,

592
00:51:35.514 --> 00:51:37.714
the organs failed.

593
00:51:39.274 --> 00:51:41.273
How long have they been missing?

594
00:51:41.313 --> 00:51:43.993
Four hours and 36 minutes.

595
00:51:44.033 --> 00:51:46.712
- They're on foot?
- Yes.

596
00:51:46.792 --> 00:51:50.512
Wade, 1.2 miles an hour,
five mile perimeter,

597
00:51:50.592 --> 00:51:53.551
- standby for suspect description.
- We're on it.

598
00:51:53.631 --> 00:51:55.031
Follow me.

599
00:52:11.228 --> 00:52:14.589
- Come on, we gotta keep going.
- I have to stop. I can't run anymore.

600
00:52:14.669 --> 00:52:15.909
- You gotta try.
- Where?

601
00:52:15.989 --> 00:52:18.387
- Anywhere but here.
- But there's nothing.

602
00:52:18.507 --> 00:52:21.147
Everything's dead, Lincoln.

603
00:52:26.587 --> 00:52:28.866
What if we are contaminated?

604
00:52:29.425 --> 00:52:31.425
Then we'd be dead.

605
00:52:32.185 --> 00:52:34.745
