It was a lie.

606
00:52:45.584 --> 00:52:48.343
- What is it?
- I don't know.

607
00:52:48.383 --> 00:52:49.982
But it's alive.

608
00:52:54.422 --> 00:52:57.302
Come on. It's mean, whatever it is.

609
00:52:57.422 --> 00:52:58.621
Let's rest in here.

610
00:52:58.701 --> 00:53:01.340
