613
00:53:06.261 --> 00:53:08.619
Forty-eight hours.
Three days maximum.

614
00:53:08.659 --> 00:53:10.339
Tell me about Six Echo.

615
00:53:10.419 --> 00:53:13.658
He was really the first one
to question his environment,

616
00:53:13.738 --> 00:53:15.178
his whole existence here.

617
00:53:15.258 --> 00:53:19.298
Over the last few months,
he began demonstrating unstable behavior

618
00:53:19.378 --> 00:53:22.098
and I can't account for it.

619
00:53:22.178 --> 00:53:24.538
