It keeps them fearful of going outside.

624
00:53:36.215 --> 00:53:40.615
The Island is the one thing
that gives them hope,

625
00:53:40.655 --> 00:53:42.615
gives them purpose.

626
00:53:43.134 --> 00:53:45.294
