They change around little details,

728
01:00:46.827 --> 01:00:48.947
but they're all pretty much the same.

729
01:00:49.027 --> 01:00:54.227
The life you think you had
before the "contamination,"

730
01:00:54.307 --> 01:00:56.625
it never happened.

731
01:00:57.865 --> 01:01:01.346
